[section Basic Worker Allocator]

[heading Description]

`basic_worker_allocator` is a __worker_allocator__ which assigns each worker it
allocates a new thread of execution.

[heading Header]

  #include <boost/act/worker_allocator/basic_worker_allocator.hpp>
  #include <boost/act/worker_allocator/basic_worker_allocator/basic_worker_allocator_fwd.hpp>


[heading Synopsis]

  class basic_worker_allocator;

[heading Model of]

* __worker_allocator__


